<plot>Day 2 is an abstract look at the events of 24 hours, for a man trying to come to terms with his place in the world. Questions are asked but not answered, problems are posed but not solved. The split screen effects that run throughout, add to the unease of the events and allow the viewer to immerse themselves, in the life of our on screen friend, as he reaches the end of another day.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?130677</url></doc>
